<plot>The queue is a film about limits. We see a perfectly rational man driven to extremes by the frustrations of modern life and an automated telephone system. A comical narration guides us through his transformation from passive customer to radicalized sociopath and violent criminal, as he is pushed to breaking point.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?584992</url></doc>
